Since this is a Hard Core Guild, you can only use +5 Items for PVP, including weapons, no mithril weapons allowed, and if the DM catches you using +6 gear, you will be kicked out of the guild!

You may NOT use items spells or special powers, if you can't hard cast it, you can't use it, and yes, that means no improved invisibility from cloaks, etc....

Special Events may modify these rules & Players may always make up their own rules for PVP, but these are the standard rules.

+5 Items Only,
No Item Usage (Including Buffit Rock),
No Potions, Healing, nor Regeneration Spells Allowed!
